<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Suggestion Processing Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555555;
        }
        ul {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
        .regards {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .regards p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Suggestion Processing Notification</h1>
        <p>Dear <strong><%= receiverName %></strong>,</p>

        <p>We want to inform you that a suggestion has been submitted regarding your studio. Here are the details:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>User Name:</strong> <%= user_name %></li>
            <li><strong>User Email:</strong> <%= user_email %></li>
            <li><strong>Reason for Suggestion:</strong> <%= reason %></li>
            <li><strong>Suggested Text:</strong> <%= suggested_text %></li>
        </ul>

        <p>Your suggestion is currently being reviewed by our team. We will keep you updated on the status of the suggestion.</p>

        <p>Thank you for your attention!</p>

        <div class="regards">
            <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>Your Company Name</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
